data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home that boasts energy efficient appliances and windows for sustainability and cost savings. The covered front porch is the perfect spot to relax and enjoy the beautiful surroundings. The attached garage provides convenient access to the home and offers ample storage space. Additionally, there is extra parking to the right of the house, would be great for a boat or RV. The deck and privacy fenced back yard provide the perfect space for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours! *** Seller is offering a warranty with Choice Home Warranty with acceptable offer!
